    <item>
      <title>西方投资者蜂拥入市，全球黄金需求突破 1000 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/world-gold-demand-tops-100-billion-as-western-investors-pile-in</link>
      <description><![CDATA[世界黄金协会称，第三季度全球黄金需求增长约 5%，创下同期最高纪录，消费额首次超过 1000 亿美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/world-gold-demand-tops-100-billion-as-western-investors-pile-in</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 30 Oct 2024 06:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>大谷精神崩溃的日本禁止交易员观看世界职业棒球大赛</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/traders-miss-ohtani-in-world-series-seen-by-12-of-japanese</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据估计，日本有 12% 的人口会收看棒球巨星大谷翔平 (Shohei Ohtani) 首次参加的世界职业棒球大赛，但有一个群体却错过了机会：东京的交易员无法通过手机或电视观看比赛。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/traders-miss-ohtani-in-world-series-seen-by-12-of-japanese</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 30 Oct 2024 05:54:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>瑞银业绩超出预期，但警告美国公投风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/ubs-results-beat-expectations-as-bank-warns-of-us-vote-risks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞银集团公布的第三季度业绩远超预期，但同时警告称，该公司将面临美国大选、利息收入下降等不利因素。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/ubs-results-beat-expectations-as-bank-warns-of-us-vote-risks</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 30 Oct 2024 05:46:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>丰田在日本和中国销量下降，而混合动力车在美国销量增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/toyota-sales-fall-in-japan-china-as-hybrids-make-gains-in-us</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管北美对混合动力汽车的需求强劲，但丰田汽车公司在日本和中国的销售仍面临一系列挑战，包括来自电动汽车品牌的竞争加剧、国内丑闻以及海外召回事件。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/toyota-sales-fall-in-japan-china-as-hybrids-make-gains-in-us</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 30 Oct 2024 04:30:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
