      <pubDate>Tue, 29 Oct 2024 15:29:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>玛鲁蒂铃木担心小型车业务需求低迷</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-29/maruti-suzuki-misses-profit-estimate-on-sluggish-auto-demand</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度最大的汽车制造商玛鲁蒂铃木印度有限公司 (Maruti Suzuki India Ltd.) 表示，由于季度利润不及预期，市场需求疲软，导致其小型乘用车的销售承压。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-29/maruti-suzuki-misses-profit-estimate-on-sluggish-auto-demand</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 29 Oct 2024 08:04:08 GMT</pubDate>
